If you are following the tutorials on fzysqr.com, you may want the tutorial version of nodechat at https://github.com/jslatts/nodechat-tutorial.

Visit http://nodechat.no.de/ to see this code in action. You can even ask node.js questions!

Here is the roadmap. Any suggestions or bug fixes are welcome.

